description: This hall of fame Anurak purrs with a rating of 60, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 300, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 3 for East, 3 for South, and Box for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [300 Votes, Hall of Fame]
